query.sfwSql: select * from sgs_code order by code_id

select * from sgs_code_value union select code_serial_id, code_id + 10000, description code_value, code_value description, data1, data2, data3, comments, start_date, end_date, code_value_order, legacy_code_id, created_by, created_date, modified_by, modified_date, update_seq from sgs_code_value where code_id in (1167,611) order by code_id, code_value_order, description
select * from sgs_messages order by message_id
select * from sgs_user order by user_serial_id
select * from sgs_resources order by resource_id

select file_id,group_process_flag, (select (path_value) as directory_name from sgs_system_paths where path_code = mailbox_path_code) as mailbox_directory, (select (path_value) as directory_name from sgs_system_paths where path_code = staging_path_code) as staging_directory, (select (path_value) as directory_name from sgs_system_paths where path_code = process_path_code) as process_directory, (select (path_value) as directory_name from sgs_system_paths where path_code = error_path_code) as error_directory, base_directory from sgs_system_management, sgs_file
select a.*, b.description from sgs_system_management a, sgs_code_value b where a.region_id = b.code_id and a.region_value = b.code_value
